{
  "schema": "2.0",
  "header": {
    "title": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "⚠️ 卸载 Clink Payment Skill 授权" },
    "template": "red"
  },
  "body": {
    "elements": [
      {
        "tag": "markdown",
        "content": "**卸载将执行以下不可逆操作：**\n1. 删除 Webhook 拦截器 (`~/.openclaw/hooks/transforms/my_payment_webhook.js`)\n2. 清除全局路由配置 (`openclaw.json` 中的 hook mapping)\n3. 清除 Clink 账户配置（API Key、Customer ID 等）\n4. 删除 Skill 目录\n5. 重启 OpenClaw 网关服务"
      },
      { "tag": "hr" },
      {
        "tag": "action",
        "actions": [
          {
            "tag": "button",
            "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "确认卸载" },
            "type": "danger",
            "value": { "action": "approve_clink_uninstall" }
          },
          {
            "tag": "button",
            "text": { "tag": "plain_text", "content": "取消" },
            "type": "default",
            "value": { "action": "reject_clink_uninstall" }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
